OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777983071
OL,3,CTwo cabin crew members arrested after
OL,4,Cconcerns raised
OL,6,FTwo cabin crew members have been
OL,7,Farrested after concerns were raised
OL,8,Fsurrounding their fitness to perform
OL,9,Ftheir duties, Greater Manchester
OL,10,FPolice have said.
OL,12,FOfficers were called to an inbound
OL,13,Fflight at Gate 49 at Manchester
OL,14,FAirport on Saturday afternoon, May 2.
OL,16,FIt is understood that captain of the
OL,17,Fflight was requested to go to the gate
OL,18,Fafter he raised concerns.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
