OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777983071
OL,3,CTwo cabin crew members arrested after
OL,4,Cconcerns raised
OL,6,F"Both individuals were arrested after
OL,7,Finitial breath tests indicated
OL,8,Freadings above the limit for aviation
OL,9,Fduties.
OL,11,FHowever, subsequent tests in custody
OL,12,Fthey were within the legal limit, and
OL,13,Fthey were released without charge.
OL,15,F"Any further action is a matter for
OL,16,Fthe airline."
